Welcome to the Ledger FreeClaiming Guide

To claim using a Ledger you will need Electrum. Electrum is needed to sign messages.
Remember: you will not be exporting/exposing your privat keys. They will stay on your ledger and there is no chance to get compromised.
You can download Electrum here: https://electrum.org/#download

Once downloaded, start Electrum. You will be greeted with the following screen:

IMG: Electrum1

